  "text": "A preliminary version of this paper was presented at the 12th International Workshop on Foundations of Coordination Languages and Self Adaptive Systems (FOCLASA 2013) and included in its proceedings [CITATION_1] . This paper extends that preliminary version with proof outlines, a better explanation of the relation between our results and their implications in practice, a new section on the role of associativity in our theory, including new results, and an improved overview of related work.",
